<h1 id="faq">FAQ</h1>
<p>When I send a message using Thunderbird, it hangs on “Copying message to Sent folder”?</p>
<ul>
  <li>Tools –&gt; Account Settings</li>
  <li>Select ‘Copies and Folders’ under your Citadel account.</li>
  <li>Look for the box that says ‘When sending messages, automatically…’ and observe that there is a checkbox below it labelled ‘Place a copy in…’</li>
  <li>Uncheck that box, click OK, and resume your happy day.</li>
</ul>

